title: A show about absolutely nothing
itunes:title: A show about absolutely nothing
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the nfl ... which is pretty slim this week. We dive into some deep nascar topics and aliens and some other nonsense. This is the offseason pod you've all been asking for.
